  line
  line `(a) in section 2, in sub-section (1), clauses (a) and (p) shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(b) in section 19, for the word “tribunal”, the words “Registrar or the High Court, as the case may`
  line `be,” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(c) in section 23, for the words “and before the Appellate Board before which”, the words “before`
  line `whom” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(d) in section 27,--`
  line
  line `(i) for the words “Appellate Board”, wherever they occur, the words “High Court” shall be`
  line substituted;
  line
  line `(ii) for the word “tribunal”, wherever it occurs, the words “Registrar or the High Court, as the`
  line `case may be,” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(e) in Chapter VII, for the Chapter heading, the Chapter heading “APPEALS” shall be`
  line substituted;
  line
  line `(f) in section 31,--`
  line
  line `(i) for the words “Appellate Board”, wherever they occur, the words “High Court” shall be`
  line substituted;
  line
  line `(ii) sub-section (3) shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(g) sections 32 and 33 shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(h) in sections 34 and 35, for the words “Appellate Board”, wherever they occur, the words “High`
  line `Court” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(i) section 36 shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(j) in section 48,--`
  line
  line `(i) for the words “Appellate Board”, at both the places where they occur, the words “High`
  line `Court” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(ii) for the word “tribunal”, the words “Registrar or the High Court, as the case may be,” shall`
  line `be substituted;`
  line
  line `(k) in sections 57 and 58, for the words “Appellate Board”, wherever they occur, the words “High`
  line `Court” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(l) in section 63, the words “the Appellate Board or” shall be omitted;`
  line
  line `(m) in section 72, for the words “Appellate Board”, wherever they occur, the words “High Court”`
  line `shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(n) in section 75, for the word “tribunal”, the words “Registrar or the High Court, as the case may`
  line `be,” shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(o) in section 87, in sub-section (2), clause (n) shall be omitted.`
