obj_root_law_sections_30_content:
  string
  line `In section 55 of the Consumer Protection Act, 2019, after`
  line `sub-section (1), the following sub-section shall be inserted, namely:--`
  line
  line `“(1A) Notwithstanding anything contained in sub-section (1), the qualifications, appointment,`
  line `term of office, salaries and allowances, resignation, removal and the other terms and conditions of`
  line `service of the President and other members of the National Commission appointed after the`
  line `commencement of the Tribunal Reforms Act, 2021, shall be governed by the provisions of the said`
  line Act.”.
